<figureCitation box="[931,990,1300,1322]" captionStart="FIGURE 2" captionStartId="3.[151,250,1950,1972]" captionTargetBox="[262,1327,1124,1911]" captionTargetId="figure@3.[242,1342,1084,1934]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURE 2. Cortona minuta A, male pygofer lobe, lateral view; B, male pygofer and segments X – XI, dorsal view; C, valve, ventral view D, subgenital plate, ventral view; E, style, dorsal view; F, G, H, connective and aedeagus, dorsal, ventral and lateral view, respectively." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/376438/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="361">Fig. 2</figureCitation>
